Fixed all five H01 findings and wrote the required report to `.review-slices/H01.fix.md`.

Changes were limited to `packages/evm` source/spec files plus the fix report:
- Cloned and normalized custom precompile arrays.
- Made add/remove precompile updates immutable.
- Fixed direct `Evm.create()` precompile mutator behavior.
- Routed trace logging through `step` events and `logger.trace`.
- Corrected the option docs examples/comments.

I did not run tests or builds, per the constraints.
